awk:
==================

q) how to print last field in a file?
ex: cat /etc/passwd | awk -F ':' '{print $NF}'



find:
===================
q) how to find a largest file in a directory?
du -a * | sort -n -r | head -1

grep:
===================
q) how to find number of occurenses of a string in recurrsive directories?
grep -oIr "praveen" . | wc -l
